<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/22207687">怎么用一句话，写出一个悲情的有诗感的爱情故事？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1063922" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">两个人,要有开始结果。诗也可，无诗词也可，无词说也可。</div>


</div>
